**Subject:** "Immediate Action Required: Your Account Has Been Limited"

**Sender:** "PayPal Service" [service@secure-payments.com](mailto:service@secure-payments.com)

**Email Body:**

> Dear Valued Customer,
>
> We have noticed some unusual activity on your PayPal account. For your protection, we have temporarily limited your account access. To restore full access, you must verify your identity by clicking the link below.
>
> **Verify Your Account Now** (hyperlink text)
>
> If you do not verify your account within 24 hours, your account will be permanently suspended. We appreciate your cooperation in this matter.
>
> Thank you,
> The PayPal Team



